{
  "stem": "22979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the evening, we had to go through the gate back to the camp-- [INAUDIBLE] was not evening it was-- late in the afternoon-- one by one, and SS on both sides, and nude.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were inspecting us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And who had only a blemish, it was right and left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the side where the-- where the-- behind the [NON-ENGLISH] where the barrack was, where the [? all-- ?] administration barrack-- [SIGHS] on one side where the wooden barracks were, one part-- and those who were marked or were [INAUDIBLE] or were exhausted or not only-- didn't look any more like human beings on one side.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other was who were-- who were to life-- to work, I mean-- slave labor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So at this time, you know, we were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we went to this side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were on the barrack 1,000, including the 300 from our commando.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we came back on the barracks, beside our 300-- we had a special barrack you know, in-- in Birkenau, in the Kanada.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Only 20 was left on the barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Almost 1,000 were killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The whole Birkenau B1 was exterminated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The girls, some of them, were pretty good, screaming and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right away, they were unloaded to the trucks and taken to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the biggest selection which I was in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You came back, the camp empty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It filled up with new arrivals from Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then they moved the men from [INAUDIBLE] B to another camp and started filling up women in-- in Birkenau-- but it was another section, again.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Children never came to-- to the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although, they came-- you know when?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
